        <div class="item-info">
                <div class="slug-wrap">
                        <h3 class="slug"><a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/">Goats and Soda</a></h3>
                </div>

            <h2 class="title"><a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2020/04/15/834666123/trump-and-who-how-much-does-the-u-s-give-whats-the-impact-of-a-halt-in-funding"  data-metrics='{"action":"Click Story Title","category":"Story List"}' >Trump And WHO: How Much Does The U.S. Give? What's The Impact Of A Halt In Funding?</a></h2>
            
            
            <p class="teaser"><a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2020/04/15/834666123/trump-and-who-how-much-does-the-u-s-give-whats-the-impact-of-a-halt-in-funding"><time datetime="2020-04-15"><span class="date">April 15, 2020 &#149; </span></time>Citing undue influence from China on the World Health Organization among other reasons, the president has said he wants to suspend U.S. funding for the global agency pending a review.</a></p>

            

        </div>
        
    </div>
</article>
