            <h2 class="title"><a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2020/04/13/826474975/coronavirus-nurses-ask-an-ebola-veteran-is-it-ok-to-be-afraid"  data-metrics='{"action":"Click Story Title","category":"Story List"}' >Coronavirus Nurses Ask An Ebola Veteran: Is It OK To Be Afraid?</a></h2>
            
            
