                <div class="slug-wrap">
                        <h3 class="slug"><a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/">Goats and Soda</a></h3>
                </div>

            <h2 class="title"><a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2020/04/10/831883664/the-new-coronavirus-appears-to-take-a-greater-toll-on-men-than-on-women"  data-metrics='{"action":"Click Story Title","category":"Story List"}' >The New Coronavirus Appears To Take A Greater Toll On Men Than On Women</a></h2>
            
            
            <p class="teaser"><a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2020/04/10/831883664/the-new-coronavirus-appears-to-take-a-greater-toll-on-men-than-on-women"><time datetime="2020-04-10"><span class="date">April 10, 2020 &#149; </span></time>Not only are a higher percentage of patients men than women, but they seem to suffer more severe symptoms. And they may be less likely to go in for testing.</a></p>

            

